text: Seppo Reijonen (born 29 April 1944) is a Finnish ski jumper. He competed in the large hill event at the 1968 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1944 births Category:Living people Category:Finnish male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Finland Category:Ski jumpers at the 1968 Winter Olympics Category:People from Sortavala
